title: BBC World Service Radio Documentary Collection
description:
A collection of BBC World Service podcasts. All can be freely downloaded from the BBC website, but this is a more convenient download if you just want an awesome collection.

Most of the files are either the 23 minute documentary format, or the little 8 minute "Witness" historical mini-docs. There are a few other random files from other programs such as From Our Own Correspondent, and Outlook that I thought were particularly interesting.

Everything is mp3 format.
